### 테스트 시나리오
### 1. 배송 생성 (주문 생성 이벤트 수신 → 배송 엔티티 생성)
### (허브 간 이동 정보 조회 -> 최종 목적지 위도/경도 조회 -> 배송 담당자 할당 API 호출)
POST http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "a3f7b70a-1111-2222-3333-444444444444",
  "startHubId": "f7a2e3d1-1111-2222-3333-444444444444",
  "endHubId": "c9d4f1b0-1111-2222-3333-444444444444",
  "deliveryAddress": "서울특별시 강남구 역삼동 123-45",
  "recipientId": "b1a4c2e3-1111-2222-3333-444444444444"
}

### 2. 배송 상세 조회 (주문 정보 포함)

GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries/{deliveryId}
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 3. 배송 전체 조회 (필터링)

### Test Case 1: 기본값 사용 (쿼리 파라미터 없음)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 2: 주문 ID와 배송 상태 필터링
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries?orderId=a3f7b70a-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&deliveryStatus=IN_TRANSIT
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 3: 시작/종료 허브 필터링
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries?startHubId=f7a2e3d1-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&endHubId=c9d4f1b0-1111-2222-3333-444444444444
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### Test Case 4: 모든 필터 조건 사용 (페이지, 사이즈, 정렬, 추가 필드)
GET http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries?page=2&size=20&orderBy=createdAt&sort=asc&orderId=a3f7b70a-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&startHubId=f7a2e3d1-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&endHubId=c9d4f1b0-1111-2222-3333-444444444444&originHubId=123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000&destinationHubId=987e6543-e21b-12d3-a456-426614174111&deliveryStatus=DELIVERED&deliveryRouteStatus=COMPLETED
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 4. 배송 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8086/api/v1/deliveries/e3b0c442-98fc-1c14-9afb-000000000001?deletedBy=1001
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json


